<i>adjective</i>: 성가시다 [성가시다], 거추장스럽다 [거ː추장스럽따] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>성가시다 [성가시다]</dt><br>
<dd>annoying; bothersome; tiresome</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것이 자꾸 못살게 굴어 괴롭고 귀찮다.</dd><br>
<dd>Painful and tired because something or someone keeps bothering one.</dd><br>
<dt>거추장스럽다 [거ː추장스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. burdensome; cumbersome; troublesome</dd><br>
<dd>물건 등이 크거나 무거워서 다루기가 어렵고 불편하다.</dd><br>
<dd>An object being big or heavy, making it difficult and uncomfortable to handle.</dd><br>
<dd>2. irritating; bothersome</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 사람 등이 귀찮고 싫다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something or someone being irritating or bothersome.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>